I've developed a comprehensive LLM Provider Key Management system with the following enhanced features:

### Supported Providers
- Anthropic
- Hugging Face
- OpenAI
- Google Gemini
- Mistral

### Security Features
- Detailed key validation
- Format-specific validation
- Encryption before storage
- Comprehensive error handling

### Monitoring Capabilities
- Prometheus Metrics
- Sentry Error Tracking
- Detailed Audit Logging
  - Key addition
  - Key validation
  - Key deletion
  - Failed validation attempts

### Access Control
- Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
- Granular Permissions
- IP and User Agent Tracking

### Key Management Features
- Periodic Key Validation
- Automatic Key Deactivation
- Comprehensive Metrics Tracking

### Monitoring Metrics
- Key Validation Attempts
- Key Usage Tracking
- Active Keys per Provider

### Security Considerations
- No plaintext key storage
- Provider-specific connectivity tests
- Automatic key deactivation after multiple failures

### Alerting Mechanisms
- Sentry Error Reporting
- Prometheus Metrics for Monitoring
- Detailed Audit Logs
